name: Security Reference Service (FII Online)
description: **Just click an 'Auto Login' button and it should log you in. Once logged in, you will see a menu on the left side. There is a button for Library Reference which allows you to query a database of Mandatory actions from 1968 to today. ** If you use the Financial Actions menu, you have access to the electronic version of the book including Active and Obsolete stocks. This is updated daily.
